## Prerequisites

- Basic statistics knowledge
- Familiarity with process improvement concepts
- Laptop with Minitab/JMP or R installed

## Statistical Tools Required

| Tool | Version | Purpose |
|------|---------|---------|
| Minitab | 21+ | Statistical analysis, DOE, SPC |
| JMP | 18+ | DOE and regression (alternative) |
| R (with RStudio) | 4.3+ | Open-source statistical computing |
| Excel | Microsoft 365 | Basic analysis and QFD matrices |

## Assessment

- Module quizzes (knowledge checks)
- Hands-on exercises with datasets (skill application)
- Phase review checkpoints (quality gates)
- DMEDI Capstone Project (integration)

## Capstone Project

Participants complete a full DMEDI project applying all phases to a real problem. Three scenario options are available:

1. Electric vehicle battery pack (product development)
2. Hospital patient flow optimization (process design)
3. Software feature development (service design)

